    <h1>OCD Quick Screen — Basic (Demo)</h1>
    <p class="lead">A very simple, non-clinical screening: answer how much each problem has bothered you in the past 2 weeks.</p>

    <form id="screenForm" novalidate>
      <!-- 5 short example questions. These are generic behaviour/check style questions only. -->
      <div class="question" data-q="1">
        <div class="q-title">1) Do you have unwanted repetitive thoughts that you can't easily ignore?</div>
        <div class="scale" role="radiogroup" aria-labelledby="">
          <!-- scale 0-4 -->
          <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="0"><span class="scale-btn">0 — Not at all</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="1"><span class="scale-btn">1 — A little</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="2"><span class="scale-btn">2 — Moderately</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="3"><span class="scale-btn">3 — Quite a bit</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="4"><span class="scale-btn">4 — Extremely</span></label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="question" data-q="2">
        <div class="q-title">2) Do you repeat behaviours (checking, washing, counting, arranging) to reduce anxiety?</div>
        <div class="scale">
          <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="0"><span class="scale-btn">0 — Not at all</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="1"><span class="scale-btn">1 — A little</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="2"><span class="scale-btn">2 — Moderately</span></label>
          <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="3"><span class="scale-btn">3 — Quite a bit</span></label>
